    "This malfunction in the VMM operation can be observed even at a small integration density of 8 × 8 CA.",
    "We also tested a 32 × 32 CA using a memristive device without selection functionality (Supplementary Fig.",
    "S4), and observed a large operational distribution in the DC I-V characteristics.",
    "Thus, accurate VMM operations for the ANN accelerator cannot be guaranteed when the memristive device integrated into the CA lacks selection functionality.",
